OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCraft beer industry faces  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhuge challenges, says MP   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The UK's brewing industry is "in real  
OL,6, crisis" due to soaring costs and       
OL,7, consumers having less disposable       
OL,8, income, an MP has warned.              
OL,10,FAbout 80 breweries called time in 2022,
OL,11,Fand one industry expert fears more than
OL,12,Ftriple that number could go this year. 
OL,14,FLabour MP Charlotte Nichols, who chairs
OL,15,Fthe All Party Parliamentary Group on   
OL,16,FPubs, has asked for targeted help.     
OL,18,FThe government said support included an
OL,19,Falcohol duty freeze and assistance with
OL,20,Fbusiness rates and energy bills.       
